From: Daijiro Fukuda <fukuda@clear-code.com>
Date: Mon, 27 Dec 2021 09:53:13 +0900
Subject: [PATCH 14/18] Fix comparison warning (#420)

This fix a comparison warning between int and size_t,
which e99498a801cc99e5d622844153e59667a1d3acc7 causes.
---
 src/modules/spell/spell-enchant.cpp | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/src/modules/spell/spell-enchant.cpp b/src/modules/spell/spell-enchant.cpp
index a553d08a..4f8d108d 100644
--- a/src/modules/spell/spell-enchant.cpp
+++ b/src/modules/spell/spell-enchant.cpp
@@ -46,7 +46,7 @@ std::vector<std::string> SpellEnchant::hint(const std::string &language,
     std::vector<std::string> result;
     number = number > limit ? limit : number;
     result.reserve(number);
-    for (auto i = 0; i < number; i++) {
+    for (size_t i = 0; i < number; i++) {
         result.push_back(suggestions[i]);
     }
 
